To make the "gem" module
========================

cd Projects/GEM/pyrite

setenv GEM_ARCH DARWIN       (-or- DARWIN64 -or- LINUX64 -or- WIN32 -or- WIN64)
setenv GEM_TYPE diamond      (-or- quartz)
setenv GEM_GRAPHICS gv

make

To run the "gem" module interactively
=====================================

cd test
   python
      import gem

      Ctrl-D        (to exit python interpreter)

To run the "gem" module in batch mode
=====================================

cd test
   python test_gem.py

   python demo_gem.py
      q             (to quit help)

   python opt_gem.py
